《'''維也納外交關係公約'''》（英語︰Vienna Convention on Diplomatic Relations<ref name="林书楷2018">{{cite book|author=林书楷|title=刑法总则|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xjqnDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA26|date=2018年9月21日|publisher=五南图书出版股份有限公司|isbn=978-957-11-9931-3|pages=26–|access-date=2020年7月27日|archive-date=2020年8月12日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812150938/https://books.google.com/books?id=xjqnDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA26|dead-url=no}}</ref>），规范的缩写为'''VCDR'''<ref name="Oelfke2018">{{cite book|author=Christian Oelfke|title=Vienna Convention on Diplomatic Relations of 18 April 1961: Commentaries on Practical Application|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JQR_DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA48|date=10 December 2018|publisher=BWV Verlag|isbn=978-3-8305-3863-9|pages=48–|access-date=2020-07-27|archive-date=2020-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730171911/https://books.google.com/books?id=JQR_DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA48|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一项界定[[独立国家|独立国家]]间[[外交关系|外交关系]]框架的[[国际条约|国际条约]]。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Bruns|first=Kai|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RWc0BwAAQBAJ|title=A Cornerstone of Modern Diplomacy: Britain and the Negotiation of the 1961 Vienna Convention on Diplomatic Relations|date=2014|publisher=Bloomsbury|isbn=978-1-62892-154-0|language=en}}</ref>條約目的是創建一套統一的外交規則，使[[外交官|外交官]]能够在不担心受到东道国胁迫或骚扰的情况下履行职责。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Vienna Convention on Diplomatic Relations|url=https://www.international.gc.ca/protocol-protocole/vienna_convention-convention_vienne.aspx?lang=eng|access-date=2022-01-06|date=2007-10-31|last=Canada|first=Global Affairs|website=international.gc.ca}}</ref>

《维也纳外交关系公约》构成了[[外交豁免权|外交豁免权]]的法律基础。该公约被广泛地视为现代[[国际关系|国际关系]]的基石<ref name="Lang2012">{{cite book|author=Michael Lang|title=Tax Rules in Non-tax Agreements|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JOu8R4gQzQ8C&pg=PA159|year=2012|publisher=IBFD|isbn=978-90-8722-147-8|pages=159–|access-date=2020-07-27|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812150959/https://books.google.com/books?id=JOu8R4gQzQ8C&pg=PA159|dead-url=no}}</ref>，於1961年4月18日於聯合國外交往來與豁免權會議中採用<ref>{{cite book|title=中华人民共和国百法大讲座|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=BNe4AAAAIAAJ|year=1994|publisher=法律出版社|isbn=978-7-5036-1518-4}}</ref>，它被認為是聯合國起草的最成功的法律文書之一。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Vienna Convention on Diplomatic Relations|url=https://legal.un.org/avl/ha/vcdr/vcdr.html|access-date=2022-01-06|publisher=United Nations}}</ref>

條約於1964年4月24日正式生效<ref name="CooperHeine2013">{{cite book|author1=Andrew F. Cooper|author2=Jorge Heine|author3=Ramesh Thakur|title=The Oxford Handbook of Modern Diplomacy|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tV9oAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA526|date=28 March 2013|publisher=OUP Oxford|isbn=978-0-19-165261-5|pages=526–|access-date=2020-07-27|archive-date=2020-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730172144/https://books.google.com/books?id=tV9oAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA526|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2018年10月，已有192个国家批准了该公约<ref name="ratifications" />。

